The paper discusses the principles of biological computing and the use of memristive devices in electronic circuits. These topics are related to neural networks (cs.NE), electronic devices (cs.ET), electromagnetism (cs.EM), systems and control (cs.SY), and circuit theory (cs.CE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
